# {{.Name}} — AI Agent Context

## Goal
Minimal asyncio program that connects to ClutchCall over QUIC and places an outbound call.

## Runtime
- Endpoint: `{{.Endpoint}}` (override via `CLUTCHCALL_ENDPOINT`)
- Service account JSON: `service_account.json` (override via `CLUTCHCALL_CREDENTIALS`)
- Native FFI: requires `libclutchcall_core_ffi.so`. Build with
  `bazel build //core:clutchcall_core_ffi.so` and set `CLUTCHCALL_LIB_PATH` to the
  resulting `.so`.

## Editing Rules
- The bindings under `clutchcall.serde` are auto-generated by
  `clutchcall/tools/apirpc_compiler/generate_bridges.py`. Never patch them by hand —
  update the schema upstream and regenerate.
- After bumping the SDK, run `clutch migrate` from this project root to surface schema
  drift before you ship.

## Common Tasks
- Capture audio frames: see `clutchcall-sdk/python/examples/test_dial.py` for the
  `audio_cb` / `event_cb` pattern.
